{"tid":905018,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"日本男子與初音未來舉辦婚禮場面隆重還有證婚人","createTime":"2018-11-16T20:41:26.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-17T13:20:13.000Z","uid":130626,"like":8,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"1e83012f1c3ef34aacdb9a8abbfd3badb97d8d5e","tid":905018,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-16T20:41:26.000Z","msg":"知道大家是否還記得這位35歲日本男子，他叫近藤顯彥，喜歡初音未來已經有10年之久了，現在終於與子女的偶像舉行了婚禮。此次一共有39位親友出席了這場特別的儀式，近藤顯彥還在推特上感謝了大家送上的支持和祝福。<br />\n新郎近藤顯彥表示10年前曾在職場受到了女性前輩的欺負而停職，導致他對三次元女性有了心理創傷，後來接觸到初音未來的歌曲得到了治愈。今年他還借助全息投影設備&ldquo;Gatebox&ldquo;和初音&rdquo;同居&ldquo;了，籌備了半年之後，他終於實現了和初音結婚的夢想。<br />\n從推特公佈的信息來看，這場婚禮非常正式，不僅有證婚人，還有交換戒指的環節。婚禮現場擺滿了初音未來的各種玩偶，足見近藤顯彥對初音未來的喜愛。<br />\n有不少網友都表達了對近藤顯彥追求自己幸福的理解和支持，部分粉絲甚至還獻上了自己繪製的&ldquo;新娘初音&rdquo;，祝賀他們喜結連理。<br />\n<img src=\"http://n.sinaimg.cn/translate/600/w600h800/20181106/Gxg7-hmhswin3982761.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fn.sinaimg.cn%2Ftranslate%2F600%2Fw600h800%2F20181106%2FGxg7-hmhswin3982761.jpg&h=5287f22b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://n.sinaimg.cn/translate/600/w600h800/20181106/6OqK-hmivixn3154965.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fn.sinaimg.cn%2Ftranslate%2F600%2Fw600h800%2F20181106%2F6OqK-hmivixn3154965.jpg&h=20f818a2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://n.sinaimg.cn/translate/250/w600h450/20181106/lEU2-hnprhzv5102035.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fn.sinaimg.cn%2Ftranslate%2F250%2Fw600h450%2F20181106%2FlEU2-hnprhzv5102035.jpg&h=ab1f5867&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://n.sinaimg.cn/translate/290/w600h490/20181106/ppsQ-hmhhnqt0212968.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fn.sinaimg.cn%2Ftranslate%2F290%2Fw600h490%2F20181106%2FppsQ-hmhhnqt0212968.jpg&h=cbfe1a49&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://n.sinaimg.cn/translate/600/w600h800/20181106/3KaW-hmivixn3154955.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fn.sinaim